<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Course Purchase Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #149ddd;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .course-details {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Course Purchase Confirmation</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= userName %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for purchasing our course. Your order has been successfully received.</p>
        
        <div class="course-details">
            <h3>Course Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Course Name:</strong> <%= courseName %></p>
            <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= orderId %></p>
            <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> Rs. <%= amount %></p>
        </div>

        <p>Our admin team will contact you shortly with further instructions and course access details.</p>
        
        <p>If you have any questions in the meantime, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SA Graphics. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 